title: Which Fantasy Running Backs Do You Want in 2019? l The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly and Danny Heifetz debate what to do with Todd Gurley, identify the key role players who could become stars, and find the 2019 version of Christian McCaffrey as they run through the most important fantasy running backs to know this season.

Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
